From c052485ac9882f7391db3ff78c0bd13f02ae98db Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: RivonClaw CI <ci@rivonclaw.com>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 23:09:28 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] vendor(openclaw): add explicit session checkpoint create rpc

Why:
- Affiliate checkpoint-based session management needs a preselected candidate checkpoint id so backend proposals can reference the exact transcript boundary before approval.

Removal:
- Drop when upstream exposes a business-neutral session checkpoint creation RPC that accepts a caller-provided checkpoint id and can be restored by checkpoint id.

Tests:
- apps/desktop/src/affiliate/affiliate-work-item.test.ts
